title: Ep. - 517 - THE REHEARSAL AND LOVE ISLAND
description:
Adam Glyn and Dax Holt from Hollywood Raw podcast help Kate review The Rehearsal on HBO and Love Island and Love Island UK (Peacock TV and Hulu).

 

The Rehearsal is a docu-comedy television series created, written, directed by and starring Nathan Fielder that explores the lengths one man will go to reduce the uncertainties of everyday life. Love Island involves a group of contestants, referred to as Islanders, living in isolation from the outside world in a villa, constantly under video surveillance.

 

 

Reality Life with Kate Casey
